 suppress low density\nstellar structures on scales $\\gtrsim\\,a$. The analysis presented here leads to\na new suggestion that clusters form by an analog of the \"slingshot mechanism\"\npreviously proposed for stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 May 2017 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Oct 2017 18:46:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-13"}
