\nfor the addition of damping in the tube dynamics framework, which leads to a\nricher set of behaviors in transition dynamics than previously explored.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 May 2017 20:32:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Feb 2019 16:06:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-04"}
