mptions on coupling and masses,\nthere is no strong long range attractive channel for nucleon-nucleon\ninteractions, so that nuclear matter at densities much smaller than that where\nnucleons strongly interact is a weakly interacting configuration of nucleons\nwith strongly interacting localized cores.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 May 2017 21:25:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-17"}
